cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV

The paper proposes a new exploration method for deep reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning and artificial intelligence (cs.LG, cs.AI). The proposed method is designed to work with on-policy methods, which are commonly used in robotics and control tasks (cs.RO, cs.SY). The experiments are conducted on MuJoCo tasks, which are commonly used in computer vision and robotics research (cs.CV). Therefore, the most likely categories are cs.LG and cs.AI, followed by cs.RO, cs.SY, and cs.CV.
